{"tid":2465313,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"許樹昌：第四輪疫情已近尾聲 籲市民注意防疫及不建議溝針","createTime":"2021-03-28T08:45:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T08:24:44.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"81cf32090121cb8270cbda3b90d21dbde9aac4ce","tid":2465313,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-28T08:45:32.000Z","msg":"許樹昌：第四波疫情已近尾聲 籲市民仍要注意防疫<br />\n<br />\n政府抗疫督導委員會專家顧問、中大呼吸系統科講座教授許樹昌，在新聞博覽館一個網上講座表示，本港第四波疫情已經接近尾聲，呼籲市民在復活節假期間，仍要注意防疫，以免假期後出現特別的群組感染，引致疫情反彈。<br />\n<br />\n許樹昌又相信，一批供港BioNTech(復必泰)疫苗，藥樽封蓋出現瑕疵的問題，可以在一星期內解決，預料已經打第一劑復必泰疫苗的市民，都可以趕及在限期內打第二劑。他又指，他本人原定在星期三打第二劑復必泰，但現在亦會稍為延後。他重申，現階段不建議市民「溝針」，指有關研究仍處於臨床階段，未有足夠數據證明有效。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2384934\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2384934&d=BSPHu9UqRwj8n7oVkU4q%2BfzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=b987d7e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2384934</a>"},{"pid":"24aedac86e2b640c29c67de2e717d72ec40d3283","tid":2465313,"uid":54930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-28T08:48:39.000Z","msg":"屌你老味未wfh過，完乜春第4波<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d26c440349ee8d675e5253def7b5aa9bd92e22c","tid":2465313,"uid":47356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-28T08:50:15.000Z","msg":"專業失德, 出過咩paper有過咩學位全部都要褫奪"},{"pid":"f6aeb6416b93feb856383c905d59e66485827419","tid":2465313,"uid":173271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-28T08:54:38.000Z","msg":"話應該溝針佢咪捉自己蟲?<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10212aed32da709f31554096900688458fa2d766","tid":2465313,"uid":340088,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-28T08:55:45.000Z","msg":"自己驚送頭"},{"pid":"6269b78516a89